		<title>BrainStation Launches Online Live Learning Across North America</title>
		<link>https://brainstation.io/blog/brainstation-launches-online-live-learning-across-north-america</link>
				<pubDate>Thu, 24 May 2018 17:56:10 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[BrainStation]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[BrainStationIO]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Community]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[brainstation]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[live online learning]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[online learning]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Online Live]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://blog.brainstation.io/?p=6699</guid>
				<description><![CDATA[<p>Attend live lectures, interact with other professionals, and get real-time feedback from Instructors — all from the comfort of your home (or office). </p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://brainstation.io/blog/brainstation-launches-online-live-learning-across-north-america">BrainStation Launches Online Live Learning Across North America</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://brainstation.io/blog">BrainStation® Blog</a>.</p>
]]></description>
								<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Good news (North) Americans: It&#8217;s now even easier to take a BrainStation course. This morning, we announced the launch of Online Live learning in all of North America.</p>
<p class="responsiveNews"><a href="https://brainstation.io/" rel="nofollow">Online Live learning</a> is a revolutionary new way to learn digital skills, with a proprietary online learning platform that lets you attend live lectures, collaborate with other professionals, and get immediate feedback from expert Instructors — just as you would in one of BrainStation’s campuses.</p>
<p>“Over the past six years, we’ve worked with over 250 industry leaders to develop an unmatched learning experience, and have trained over 50,000 professionals in our campuses in New York, Toronto, and Vancouver. With Online Live learning, we have combined proven instructor-led, collaborative learning with the convenience of an online experience, to really provide an engaging, effective alternative to ‘learn at your own pace’ learning models,” said Jason Field, our Founder and CEO,  <a href="http://www.prweb.com/releases/2018/05/prweb15513469.htm">in a press release</a>:</p>
<p>Check out this video to take a look at Online Live learning in action:</p>
<p><iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/261308571?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0" width="640" height="360" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our intensive full-time <a href="https://brainstation.io/course/data-science-bootcamp">Data Science</a>, <a href="https://brainstation.io/course/web-development-immersive">Web Development</a>, and <a href="https://brainstation.io/course/user-experience-immersive">User Experience Design</a> programs are all available through the Online Live learning platform. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We are also offering the <a href="https://brainstation.io/courses#online">following part-time courses</a>: </span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">iOS Development</span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Product Management</span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">User Experience</span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">User Interface Design</span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Digital Marketing</span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Social Media Marketing</span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> SEO/SEM and Analytics </span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Data Analytics and Data Science</span></li>
</ul>
<p>So don&#8217;t let your schedule keep you from learning new digital kills. The future of learning is here.</p>
